  "response": "\"Quora\" is the name of a popular online platform where people can ask questions, share knowledge, and engage in discussions on a wide range of topics. It was founded in 2009 by former Facebook employees Adam D'Angelo and Charlie Cheever. The name \"Quora\" doesn't have a specific meaning; it's simply a made-up word chosen for the platform.",
